# Wide dashboard — hero screenshot (layout 2: all columns + full wordmark)
Output tools/vhs/.render.gif

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1500
Set Height 820
Set Padding 20

Hide
Type "sh tools/vhs/.demo/run.sh"
Enter
Sleep 9s
Type "3"
Sleep 1s
Show
Sleep 2s
Screenshot assets/dashboard.png
Sleep 1s
